				<td colspan="2"><span>Yes you will do less dmg with the TDoK equiped.  I've never noticed using H2H with the drum is equiped.  I still hit with my off hand weapon, just not as often.  I have H2H max and I hit for 16 tops. (That's not counting the crits) I think it's only H2H when you just have the instrument equiped.  Well that's how I raised mine.
<br />

<br />
If your in a raid situation without the epic, then yes the mod  makes up for the lack of bard melee. (What little melee we have to begin with)  Even if you have the epic sometimes it's a good idea to use it when playing an AE Resist song.  
<br />

<br />
2.8 + .6 for IM3 (If you have it) = great resists
<br />

<br />
